Video speed control for all HTML5 video. Save your time watching videos with maximum efficiency!

Speed ​​up or slow down any HTML5 video on any website, support keyboard shortcuts to speed up or slow down videos.

Video Speed ​​Controller is a playback speed regulator for online videos, support a wide range of playback speeds from 0.25x to 16x, allow you to easily manage the playback speed when watching videos.

Video Speed ​​Controller can speed up or slow down playback on Netflix, Amazon Prime Video, Youtube and all other websites with video functions.

Video Speed ​​Controller allows you to speed up or slow down any video while playing, regardless of any standards or restrictions. You have the power to increase or decrease the playback speed, and can fast forward or rewind the video multiple times.


Main features:
- Support any HTML5 video on any website;
- Control the video playback speed with an accuracy of up to 1%;
- Simple and intuitive interface, easy to use;
- Support keyboard shortcuts to change the playback speed.
